OL,3,C'Scandal waiting to happen': One in 9
OL,4,Cnew homes built in flood risk areas
OL,6,FOne in nine new homes in England were
OL,7,Fbuilt in flood-prone areas between
OL,8,F2022 and 2024, according to a new
OL,9,Fstudy.
OL,11,FThe analysis carried out by insurer
OL,12,FAviva reveals that 11% of the 396,602
OL,13,Fnew homes in England built over the
OL,14,Fperiod were built in areas of medium
OL,15,For high risk of flooding, while more
OL,16,Fthan a quarter (26%) have some flood
OL,17,Frisk.
