OL,3,C'Scandal waiting to happen': One in 9
OL,4,Cnew homes built in flood risk areas
OL,6,FAviva warned its analysis, based on
OL,7,Fnew homes address data and the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency's latest assessment
OL,9,Fof flooding risk at a constituency
OL,10,Flevel, showed a rising proportion of
OL,11,Fnew homes are being built in flood
OL,12,Frisk areas.
OL,14,FPrevious analysis by the insurance
OL,15,Fcompany based had shown one in 13 new
OL,16,Fhomes were built in flood risk zones
OL,17,Fin the decade to 2022.
