OL,3,C'Scandal waiting to happen': One in 9
OL,4,Cnew homes built in flood risk areas
OL,6,FHomes built since 2009 are excluded
OL,7,Ffrom Flood Re, to prevent building in
OL,8,Fflood risk areas.
OL,10,FWhile comparable statistics have not
OL,11,Fbeen published since 2022, Aviva said
OL,12,Fits assessment showed the number of
OL,13,Fhomes built in flood risk areas has
OL,14,Faccelerated as housebuilding increases.
OL,16,FThe problem is particularly acute in
OL,17,Fand around the capital, the analysis
OL,18,Freveals.
