OL,6,FA third (32%) of the constituencies
OL,7,Fwith the highest number of new homes
OL,8,Fbuilt in high or medium flood risk
OL,9,Fareas between 2022 and 2024 are in
OL,10,FGreater London or Essex.
OL,12,FThe issue could be made worse by
OL,13,Fclimate change, with the UK expected
OL,14,Fto see more sudden downpours and flash
OL,15,Fflooding.
