OL,3,C'Scandal waiting to happen': One in 9
OL,4,Cnew homes built in flood risk areas
OL,6,FAviva estimated that by 2050, one in
OL,7,Fseven of the homes built between 2022
OL,8,Fand 2024 will be at high or medium
OL,9,Frisk of flooding as extreme weather
OL,10,Fworsens, and almost a third will face
OL,11,Fsome kind of flood risk.
OL,13,FAviva boss Jason Storah said that
OL,14,Fwhile the company was supportive of
OL,15,Fgovernment efforts to build more homes
OL,16,F` with Labour pledging to construct
OL,17,F1.5 million during this Parliament `
OL,18,Fit was "vital" they were built in the
OL,19,Fright place.
